::Prowl/Firearm::

Prowl's face gets sad at the mention of Striker's team. They were all
either missing or gone, and Prowl didn't think he'd see them again.

"Yeah, I guess I'm the last one." He replies, "Hey, is that your ship
that just landed? We might have some use for it here."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Firearm jumps out of the CR chamber when it finishes repairing, aiming
his arm cannon at Rubble.

"Who're you? Identify yourself!" he orders, ready to fire.
